<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= title || 'Login' %></title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #33b5e5 0, #0f172a 45%, #020617 100%);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .login-card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 460px;
      padding: 10px;
      animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(15px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .card {
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 35px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.45);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.92);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .card-header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
      padding: 22px 22px 16px;
    }

    .brand-icon {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #22c55e);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #0b1120;
      font-size: 32px;
      margin: 0 auto 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.45);
    }

    .card-title-main {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .card-subtitle-main {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 18px 22px 20px;
    }

    .tha-id-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.25);
      color: #99f6e4;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .tha-id-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
    }

    .btn-thaid {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #22c55e);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 11px 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      width: 100%;
      color: #0b1120;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.45);
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, filter 0.18s ease;
    }

    .btn-thaid:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      filter: brightness(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.60);
    }

    .btn-thaid:active {
      transform: translateY(0px) scale(0.99);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
    }

    .btn-thaid-icon {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .helper-text {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .card-footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      padding: 9px 16px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="login-card">
    <div class="card border-0">

      <div class="card-header text-center bg-transparent">
        <div class="brand-icon">
          🪪
        </div>
        <div class="card-title-main">เข้าสู่ระบบด้วย ThaID</div>
        <div class="card-subtitle-main">ระบบยืนยันตัวตนดิจิทัลภาครัฐ</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="tha-id-badge">
          <span class="tha-id-dot"></span>
          <span>เชื่อมต่อกับ Thai Digital ID (ThaID)</span>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-danger py-2 mb-3"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="post" action="/auth/login">
          <div class="mb-2">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-thaid">
              <span class="btn-thaid-icon">🔐</span>
              <span>เข้าระบบด้วย ThaID</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <p class="helper-text">
            เมื่อกดปุ่มระบบจะพาไปยังหน้าจอยืนยันตัวตนของแอป ThaID เพื่อยืนยันตัวตนของคุณ
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="card-footer text-center">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Admin Panel · รองรับการยืนยันตัวตนด้วย ThaID
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
